      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAYDEN'S GIFT (3) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 3rd at Capalaba over 366m. Top prospect. LAKODA FOCUS (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (22.14) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Should play a prominent role. HOPE'S JACKY (2) goes very well over this trip including two wins. Comes off a (23.72) win last time, scoring by 1.3 lengths in a Grade 5 over 407m at Rockhampton. Looks one of the chances. SIR BAREFOOT (8) scored by 3 lengths last time (19.88) in a Grade 4/5 over 366m at Capalaba. Has two wins already from this draw.",
